1. *Haljinu* je nosila na večeri. (She wore the dress at the evening.) 
2. Ona je lepo isplela *haljinu*. (She nicely braided the dress.)
3. *Haljina* je bila savršena za njenu figuru. (The dress was perfect for her figure.)
4. On je izabrao boju *haljine*. (He chose the color of the dress.)
5. To je najbolja *haljina* koju sam ikada videla. (This is the best dress I have ever seen.)